~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
#				SD Text editor					#
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Install and setup
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* You will need to install 'libqt4-dev':
	- "sudo apt-get install libqt4-dev"

* Extract the archive and run "qmake" in the archive root
(that's where Conf.pro is located)

* Go into the 'backend_src' folder and run make
(this will create "lib-backend.so" which is needed in order
to compile the frontend)

* Go back to the archive root and run make. This should
create the "sd_editor" binary.

* ./sd_editor and enjoy!

Matei & Matei
